On one hand, I=E2=80=99m always grumpy when companies decrease the amount o=
f information they are disclosing; on the other hand, this specific number =
is read into so deeply that I=E2=80=99m honestly not sure how much value it=
 provides other than to speculators. Of course not giving a prediction may =
only make the swings worse, but, as Netflix does fairly note, the company=
=E2=80=99s monetization capabilities will, particularly with the addition o=
