That noted, one couldn=E2=80=99t escape the feeling that the positive numbe=
rs had the same psychological impact on Netflix=E2=80=99s executives: both =
the letter to shareholders and earnings interview ( https://seekingalpha.co=
m/article/4547337-netflix-inc-nflx-q3-2022-earnings-call-transcript ) were =
